name: alloc::collections::btree::navigate::<impl collections::btree::node::NodeRef<collections::btree::node::marker::Immut<'a>, K, V, collections::btree::node::marker::LeafOrInternal>>::range_search
doc:
Finds the pair of leaf edges delimiting a specific range in a tree.

 The result is meaningful only if the tree is ordered by key, like the tree
 in a `BTreeMap` is.
